CamClare13.Transcription:
A Jake Juggelar that guggyls with a cakeEtyng vp fleche Blod &
                    Bouse I Beshero your pate
CamClare13.Note:
Added (by a hand of the late fifteenth century) to lower margin of page
                    in a Homilies of Pope Gregory.
